name: Mercury, arise!
description: From the "Earth and her daughters" cycle. Part of a commission for digital artist @johnowhitaker to create audio loops to accompany his AI art. The piece leads with throbbing percussion and brooding strings. A plaintive melody emerges before subsiding again into the horizon. The piece was composed on a Roland JDxi with a blend of digital and analog synthesis. Please contact me via Twitter for commissions.
